---

<div class="custom-info-contact text-white">
  <h1 class="heading-1">
    <span>Vamos a</span>
    <br />
    <span>conversar</span>
  </h1>
  <div>
    <div class="contact__list-wrap">
      <ul class="list mod--contact">
        <li class="list__item mod--contact">
          <div>Cotiza tus servicios con atención personalizada</div>
        </li>
        <li class="list__item mod--contact">
          <div>Te responderemos en menos de 24 horas</div>
        </li>
        <li class="list__item mod--contact">
          <div>Firmaremos un acuerdo de privacidad si así lo requieres</div>
        </li>
        <li class="list__item mod--contact">
          <div>Acceso a especialistas en producción</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="columns mod--contact-video">
    <section class="columns__col mod--contact-video">
      <div class="contact__video-address">
        <div class="contact-video">
          <div class="hf-frame">
            <div class="hf-frame-bg"></div>
            <div class="hf-streak hf-streak-1"></div>
            <div class="hf-streak hf-streak-2"></div>
            <div class="hf-streak hf-streak-3"></div>
            <div class="hf-grain"></div>
            <div class="hf-chrome-gloss"></div>
            <div class="hf-chrome-reflect"></div>
            <div class="hf-fresnel-left"></div>
            <div class="hf-fresnel-right"></div>
            <div class="hf-frame-shadow"></div>
            <div class="hf-glow"></div>
            <div class="hf-sweep"></div>
            <div class="hf-sweep-2"></div>
            <img src="/logo_metalico.avif" alt="METALICO" class="hf-logo" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info-wrap">
          <span class="contact-title">Contacto directo:</span>
          <span class="contact-mail">contacto@metalico.mx</span>
          <span class="contact-phone">
            <a href="tel:+525581082193" class="contact-link">Tel: 55 8108 2193</a>
          </span>
          <span class="contact-phone">
            <a href="https://wa.me/525581082193" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">WhatsApp: 55 8108 2193</a>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
